{"tid":519327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普向「美國國師」班農發律師信","createTime":"2018-01-04T08:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T10:35:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd5a99c4317da6baad520074d1040073cc15b18","tid":519327,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=985335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D985335&d=JSzv5puKCyEP%2Bw%2Ffh5mnCWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=0167a03c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=985335</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普向班農發律師信要求不要發表貶低他的家人及總統言論<br />\n04.01.2018 12:22<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普的代表律師向白宮前首席策略師班農，發出律師信，要求他不要發表一些貶低他的家人及總統的言論。特朗普代表律師的聲明中提到，班農在一本即將出版有關白宮內幕的書所提到的內容，將會引起許多法律訴訟，包括誹謗及違反保密協議，指法律行動迫在眉睫。<br />\n<br />\n一本即將在美國出版、聲稱披露白宮內幕的新書，引述班農說，特朗普的兒子小特朗普，在一六年與競選團隊成員，會晤一名俄羅斯律師是叛國及不愛國。特朗普發表聲明，指班農被開除時，不單失去工作，亦都失去理智。"},{"pid":"ae589c012357586c5eb73d2166ba15d277e2d0c1","tid":519327,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fd3b41c4455781ea14b043de777442b7ac6526","tid":519327,"uid":13718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<br />\n遲下nineup報可以做埋政治版<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a799910814c0dbaf33677f8f8ba28ef41540d631","tid":519327,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"25"}]}